<Content>Excellent hotel Have just returned from a 5 night stay at this lovely hotel. The room was bright and airy, with a comfortable bed and spotless bathroom - in fact this was one of the cleanest hotels I've ever stayed in. The breakfast was delicious and plentiful, catering for all tastes. The location is perfect; a pleasant stroll to all main sights or very handy for the U and S Bahn. There are lots of excellent eating places nearby. Our favourite was the Steakhaus Asador, just round the corner on Wilhelmstrasse (turn right at the top of Anhalter - look out for the fairy lights on the left). 
